aboutUs: At LT Drain and Small Repair, we are a team of highly skilled and experienced plumbing professionals dedicated to providing top-notch service to the residents of Wilmer and Mobile, AL. Our expertise spans a wide range of plumbing services, from water heater maintenance and faucet installations to drain cleaning and whole-house repiping. With our local presence and in-depth knowledge of the area, we are uniquely equipped to handle all your plumbing needs efficiently and effectively.
